column5: Winchester SX4 Hybrid Hunter 20 Gauge Shotgun
column7: The Winchester SX4 Hybrid Hunter 20 Gauge Shotgun features a crossbolt safety and an Inflex technology recoil pad.
column23: The Winchester SX4 Hybrid Hunter 20 Gauge Shotgun has a 26-inch barrel and an aluminum alloy receiver. It also has a crossbolt safety, a fixed Truglo fiber optic front sight and a 3+1 capacity.

column23: Elevate your Cleveland Cavaliers style with this Columbia Omni-Wick Outward Nine Quarter-Zip Pullover Top This lightweight pullover is perfect for mild temperatures and the Omni-Shade technology will protect you from the sun's harmful rays The heat-sealed Cleveland Cavaliers graphics show your team spirit and the contrast color zippers add a stylish touch  Whether you're at Rocket Mortgage FieldHouse or watching from home this pullover will keep you comfortable and protected from the sun while you cheer on the Cleveland Cavaliers

column5: Browning X-Bolt HC McMillan LR .300 PRC Bolt-Action Rifle
column7: The Browning X-Bolt HC McMillan LR .300 PRC Bolt-Action Rifle has a 3+1-round capacity and a top tang safety with a bolt unlock button.
column23: The Browning X-Bolt HC McMillan LR .300 PRC Bolt-Action Rifle has an applied Cerakote finish, an OVIX McMillan Game Scout stock, a 26-inch fluted, heavy sporter barrel and a 20 MOA Picatinny rail. This firearm also features a 3+1-round capacity, a Recoil Hawg muzzle brake and a top tang safety with a bolt unlock button.

column287: The Browning X-Bolt HC McMillan LR .300 PRC Bolt-Action Rifle has a 3+1-round capacity and a top tang safety with a bolt unlock button.
column303: The Browning X-Bolt HC McMillan LR .300 PRC Bolt-Action Rifle has an applied Cerakote finish, an OVIX McMillan Game Scout stock, a 26-inch fluted, heavy sporter barrel and a 20 MOA Picatinny rail. This firearm also features a 3+1-round capacity, a Recoil Hawg muzzle brake and a top tang safety with a bolt unlock button.

column5: Mossberg SA 28 Gauge Semiautomatic Shotgun
column7: The Mossberg SA 28 Gauge Semiautomatic Shotgun features a semiautomatic action with a 4+1 firing capacity and a 26-inch vent-rib barrel.
column19: Practice your shooting skills with the Mossberg SA 28 Gauge Semiautomatic Shotgun. This weapon features a semiautomatic action with a 4+1 firing capacity, as well as a 26-inch vent-rib barrel. This shotgun also includes a synthetic stock and fixed sights and front bead sights.

column7: The Winchester SX4 Super Compact 20 Gauge Shotgun features a 2 position crossbolt safety and an Inflex technology recoil pad.
column23: The Winchester SX4 Super Compact 20 Gauge Shotgun has a semi-auto action and an aluminum alloy receiver. It also has a 2 position crossbolt safety, a fixed Truglo fiber optic front sight and an invector choke system.

column303: The Winchester SX4 Super Compact 20 Gauge Shotgun has a semi-auto action and an aluminum alloy receiver. It also has a 2 position crossbolt safety, a fixed Truglo fiber optic front sight and an invector choke system.

column23: The Sako S20 Hunter 6.5 PRC Bolt Rifle has a 24-inch threaded barrel and a 2-stage safety. It also has a synthetic Roughtech stock, full aluminum bedding and a Tri-Lug 60-degree bolt-throw.

column303: The Tikka T3X CTR 6.5 Creedmoor Bolt Action Rifle is built with a threaded steel barrel and a synthetic stock with an interchangeable grip and a soft recoil pad. It has a 10+1 round capacity and comes with a 2-position safety.

column23: Stay protected from the elements while cheering on the Houston Astros with this Columbia Flash Forward Challenger Omni-Shade Full-Zip Windbreaker This lightweight windbreaker is perfect for mild temperatures featuring water-resistant fabric and UPF 40 sun protection The full-zip design and scuba hood with drawstring provide added comfort while the embroidered Houston Astros graphics proudly display your team spirit  Whether you're at Minute Maid Park or just out and about this windbreaker will keep you protected from the elements while showing off your Astros pride

column7: The Christensen Arms Ridgeline FFT Titanium 7mm Remington Magnum Bolt Action Rifle features a carbon fiber wrapped barrel with threading.
column23: The Christensen Arms Ridgeline FFT Titanium 7mm Remington Magnum Bolt Action Rifle is a tactical firearm featuring a carbon fiber wrapped barrel and a synthetic stock with metallic accents. Its barrel is threaded, and it also comes with a removeable brake.

column23: Stay warm and show your Chicago Blackhawks pride with this Columbia Benton Springs Half-Snap Jacket This midweight pullover features embroidered Chicago Blackhawks graphics and is made from MTR fleece fabric for maximum warmth The elastic cuffs and mock collar provide a comfortable fit while the four snap placket and front and back yoke seams add a touch of style  This pullover is perfect for any Chicago Blackhawks fan looking to stay warm and stylish on game day

column5: Tristar Products Sporting Arms Viper G2 .410 Bore Semiautomatic Shotgun
column7: The Tristar Products Sporting Arms Viper G2 .410 Bore Semiautomatic Shotgun features a high-grade Turkish walnut stock and a rubber recoil pad.
column23: The Tristar Products Sporting Arms Viper G2 .410 Bore Semiautomatic Shotgun is a 5-round shotgun featuring a blued barrel, a cerakote-finished receiver and a Turkish walnut stock. It also boasts a fixed fiber optic sight. The firearm comes with a choke box, wrench and shim kit.

column303: The Tristar Products Sporting Arms Viper G2 .410 Bore Semiautomatic Shotgun is a 5-round shotgun featuring a blued barrel, a cerakote-finished receiver and a Turkish walnut stock. It also boasts a fixed fiber optic sight. The firearm comes with a choke box, wrench and shim kit.

column7: The Sako S20 Hunter 7mm Rem Mag Bolt Rifle features a 24-inch threaded barrel and full aluminum bedding.
column23: The Sako S20 Hunter 7mm Rem Mag Bolt Rifle has a 24-inch threaded barrel and a 2-stage safety. It also has a receiver integrated Picatinny rail, full aluminum bedding and a Tri-Lug 60-degree bolt-throw.
